Description: The fdacluster package provides the kma function that 
    jointly performs clustering and alignment of a functional 
    data set (unidimensional or multidimensional). The warping is 
    parametric. Currently supported classes of warping functions 
    are shift, dilation and affine transformations. The algorithm 
    is fully parallelized.
